{"tid":186880,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] 新買既ssd write speed出奇地慢","createTime":"2017-04-04T13:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T23:47:46.000Z","uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ae46f1e7661079b6f1dd1d67eb3556305cee9ec","tid":186880,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:49:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ARq6585.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FARq6585.png&h=346d1210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新買既kingston uv400 120gb<br />\n今日岩岩新換上去部2010 macbook小白度<br />\nspeed test一開始write係200mb左右，一路係咁跌到test完<br />\n但read就正常<br />\n<br />\n已經開埋trim，但結果一樣<br />\n<br />\nssd插原本hdd個位，hdd插cd個位<br />\n我知部機剩係support sata2，但無理由個速度會咁？<br />\n<br />\n到底係咩原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dde72485436584a75eb40e899ad8269d45adcea","tid":186880,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"997e9aac36087574bfda0b579b58dcc8eefab3de","tid":186880,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:15:19.000Z","msg":"有冇restart試過？"},{"pid":"7193a759c183d2aa790d291769421bec2ad2b7bd","tid":186880,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:20:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇restart試過？</blockquote><br />\n試過幾次，都係咁<br />\n<br />\nboot機時間係比之前用hdd快左（撳制到入pw畫面18秒左右）<br />\n開app都快過之前<br />\n咁樣應該即係read speed冇問題？<br />\n<br />\n但就係唔明點解write speed一開始測果陣係200mb，之後就keep住跌到完test，跌到去70幾mb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2bc334b27b893ddc5374f2aba2b2b0b674d2e16","tid":186880,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d700c2ec2b2bfa158594941ce09eca6209ee9d6d","tid":186880,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:41:42.000Z","msg":"就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b95978c0c9b7432cc5c96bd65fb7c86bc88a04a","tid":186880,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:14:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新買架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果真係就死咁我應該都可以拎到去換／保養？<br />\n<br />\n但我想知係我settings問題定係hardware問題，定真係隻ssd有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"3075bd6a446a504f32cefdfe6a6905dd7da00fb0","tid":186880,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:12:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新買架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果真係就死咁我應該都可以拎到去換／保養？<br />\n<br />\n但我想知係我settings問題定係hardware問題，定真係隻ssd有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n裝ssd, 應該冇setting要搞，最多開trim<br />\n<br />\n會唔會係個speedtest tool唔準<br />\n<br />\n又或者真係ssd壞<br />\n<br />\n2010 macbook sata 2應該做到 2xx read and write<br />\n<br />\n不過點講OS一定快過hdd，因為SSD 4K快先係最重要"},{"pid":"8e1291d0e1a7ceeaf13fedf2c285e6d7b910dcf6","tid":186880,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:19:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新買架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果真係就死咁我應該都可以拎到去換／保養？<br />\n<br />\n但我想知係我settings問題定係hardware問題，定真係隻ssd有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n裝ssd, 應該冇setting要搞，最多開trim<br />\n<br />\n會唔會係個speedtest tool唔準<br />\n<br />\n又或者真係ssd壞<br />\n<br />\n2010 macbook sata 2應該做到 2xx read and write<br />\n<br />\n不過點講OS一定快過hdd，因為SSD 4K快先係最重要</blockquote><br />\n岩岩再erase過隻ssd，再重裝el capitan<br />\n之後再用trimforce個方法開trim<br />\n跟住再test<br />\n<br />\n今次write keep住係200，read就23x<br />\n應該冇問題了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93e0e51b7616066f18e5763aeb054d7bf31feb2","tid":186880,"uid":82970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:53:14.000Z","msg":"到底有冇4K對齊?"},{"pid":"b42eb52058b5379c37970ddbdfd5c782a2fff451","tid":186880,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:02:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到底有冇4K對齊?</blockquote><br />\ngoogle過下<br />\n好似話format隻ssd做mac os journaled果陣佢自己已經會搞掂，唔洗再4k對齊<br />\n<br />\n雖然依家搞掂左，但都唔知到底係咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714af0609ec05f75a16780ab254c3420abb9c13d","tid":186880,"uid":11721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:39:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇restart試過？</blockquote><br />\n試過幾次，都係咁<br />\n<br />\nboot機時間係比之前用hdd快左（撳制到入pw畫面<span style=\"color: red;\">18秒</span>左右）<br />\n開app都快過之前<br />\n咁樣應該即係read speed冇問題？<br />\n<br />\n但就係唔明點解write speed一開始測果陣係200mb，之後就keep住跌到完test，跌到去70幾mb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d4bc340e117883aa98951ea110327c5a396355","tid":186880,"uid":37380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:40:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇restart試過？</blockquote><br />\n試過幾次，都係咁<br />\n<br />\nboot機時間係比之前用hdd快左（撳制到入pw畫面<span style=\"color: red;\">18秒</span>左右）<br />\n開app都快過之前<br />\n咁樣應該即係read speed冇問題？<br />\n<br />\n但就係唔明點解write speed一開始測果陣係200mb，之後就keep住跌到完test，跌到去70幾mb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb20d841aad01f6291230fa07eec770efd7dab0c","tid":186880,"uid":11721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:43:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇restart試過？</blockquote><br />\n試過幾次，都係咁<br />\n<br />\nboot機時間係比之前用hdd快左（撳制到入pw畫面<span style=\"color: red;\">18秒</span>左右）<br />\n開app都快過之前<br />\n咁樣應該即係read speed冇問題？<br />\n<br />\n但就係唔明點解write speed一開始測果陣係200mb，之後就keep住跌到完test，跌到去70幾mb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nI mean姐係隻野冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3b9b58c1ec17cf961f7fec85142f73dfe4a9ef","tid":186880,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:47:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇restart試過？</blockquote><br />\n試過幾次，都係咁<br />\n<br />\nboot機時間係比之前用hdd快左（撳制到入pw畫面<span style=\"color: red;\">18秒</span>左右）<br />\n開app都快過之前<br />\n咁樣應該即係read speed冇問題？<br />\n<br />\n但就係唔明點解write speed一開始測果陣係200mb，之後就keep住跌到完test，跌到去70幾mb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都知18秒好慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我係youtube睇人地boot time d片都係差唔多時間（～10秒，sata2應該做唔到10秒內？）<br />\n同埋依家佢read/write都正常就算了，反正都好少熄機，廢事越搞越衰<br />\n<br />\n仲有我個hdd插緊果個轉接架好似得sata1，唔知會唔會係佢拖慢左個boot time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個架幾年前買落，可能中左伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea361cadb52055d176d685fdf4c53660dd48c840","tid":186880,"uid":11721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:48:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇restart試過？</blockquote><br />\n試過幾次，都係咁<br />\n<br />\nboot機時間係比之前用hdd快左（撳制到入pw畫面<span style=\"color: red;\">18秒</span>左右）<br />\n開app都快過之前<br />\n咁樣應該即係read speed冇問題？<br />\n<br />\n但就係唔明點解write speed一開始測果陣係200mb，之後就keep住跌到完test，跌到去70幾mb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nI mean姐係隻野冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但uv400最少都300MBps 冇理由200"},{"pid":"3a450a2bbd932f21f649316b72a26a97ac5d5366","tid":186880,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:50:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇restart試過？</blockquote><br />\n試過幾次，都係咁<br />\n<br />\nboot機時間係比之前用hdd快左（撳制到入pw畫面<span style=\"color: red;\">18秒</span>左右）<br />\n開app都快過之前<br />\n咁樣應該即係read speed冇問題？<br />\n<br />\n但就係唔明點解write speed一開始測果陣係200mb，之後就keep住跌到完test，跌到去70幾mb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nI mean姐係隻野冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁我都放心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔該晒咁多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c48e7e98c6d25f7d3715f5d3ebdeb448bec7b48","tid":186880,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:55:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇restart試過？</blockquote><br />\n試過幾次，都係咁<br />\n<br />\nboot機時間係比之前用hdd快左（撳制到入pw畫面<span style=\"color: red;\">18秒</span>左右）<br />\n開app都快過之前<br />\n咁樣應該即係read speed冇問題？<br />\n<br />\n但就係唔明點解write speed一開始測果陣係200mb，之後就keep住跌到完test，跌到去70幾mb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nI mean姐係隻野冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但uv400最少都300MBps 冇理由200</blockquote><br />\nSata2 應該係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我果隻120gb，如果買大d又好似會快少少<br />\n<br />\n不過唔緊要啦，最緊要係知道隻ssd冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4d3e90632ba0acbe8b3e8179b814c45ce440d4","tid":186880,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T20:52:21.000Z","msg":"之前隻mx300都係咁，我上左代理換"},{"pid":"847639f90d300e060f55331013091da8ab1eab7a","tid":186880,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T23:47:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前隻mx300都係咁，我上左代理換</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我用一排試下先<br />\n<br />\n如果再出現呢個情況就拎去換<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}